  <p>
An 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_independent_mental_capacity_advocate">Independent Mental Capacity Advocate</xref>
 is a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_person">PERSON</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
An 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_independent_mental_capacity_advocate">Independent Mental Capacity Advocate</xref>
 (
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_independent_mental_capacity_advocate">IMCA</xref>
) assists people who lack mental capacity to express their views.  </p>
  <p>
For further information on 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_independent_mental_capacity_advocate">Independent Mental Capacity Advocates</xref>
, see the Office of Public Guardian and 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_department_of_health_and_social_care">Department of Health and Social Care</xref>
 part of the 
    <xref href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/independent-mental-capacity-advocates"
            scope="external"
            format="html">gov.uk website.</xref>
  </p>

